                    <span>A darker print would make this book easier to read.  I agree that this is an excellent source for how to do things in SQL.  
<br />
<br />Know that the DB2 on the CD rom is past the deadline for being operational.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">DB2 software on CD-ROM expired Nov 2004</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
